INSERT INTO `sys_oper_log` VALUES (128, '文章管理', 1, 'com.ruoyi.system.controller.TextTableController.addSave()', 'POST', 1, 'admin', '超级管理员', '/system/text_control/add', '127.0.0.1', '内网IP', '{\"textname\":[\"一个人，一座庙\"],\"textcontent\":[\"<p style=\\\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Tahoma; font-size: 16px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 16px; overflow: hidden; padding: 0px;\\\">只要是去大山深处的项目分队，总喜欢爬爬山，出出汗，是工作需要，也为一探究竟。习惯了在山里跋涉，爬山也就变成了享受。</p><p style=\\\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Tahoma; font-size: 16px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 16px; overflow: hidden; padding: 0px;\\\">\\r\\n\\t　　徽县大石湾，一个地形陡峭、溶洞众多的石灰岩山区，分队新发现的矿脉和前人采矿的老硐，都位于高高的山腰之上。</p><p style=\\\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Tahoma; font-size: 16px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 16px; overflow: hidden; padding: 0px;\\\">\\r\\n\\t　　早早就上路了，沿着崎岖的山路，一路行来，一路感慨。新竹，蔷薇，幽兰，野花，时时的新奇，乍现的景致，黝深的矿洞，巨大的采坑，复杂的现象，奇妙的表现。思索，探知，交流，归纳，不曾失去趣味，更增看景<a href=\\\"http://www.meiwenjx.com/duanpianmeiwen/xinqingduanwen/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" style=\\\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\\\">心情</a>。</p><p style=\\\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Tahoma; font-size: 16px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 16px; overflow: hidden; padding: 0px;\\\">\\r\\n\\t　　远观怪石嶙峋危岩险峻，近看树奇枝异藤蔓垂青，崇山叠翠满目清新，松竹遍野花香扑鼻，未曾见过的各色野花，形态迥异的石上青苔，山泉流瀑似白练垂悬，鸟语鸣啭听空谷传音，伴着幽绿，闻着清香，美景入眼，乐趣无穷。</p><p style=\\\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Tahoma; font-size: 16px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 16px; overflow: hidden; padding: 0px;\\\">\\r\\n\\t　　高高的山崖下，陡峻的半山上，工作之余，不期而遇了一座小庙，一个只有一个和尚的小庙。</p><p><span style=\\\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Tahoma; font-size: 16px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 28px;\\\">\\r\\n</span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Tahoma; font-size: 16px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 28px;\\\">\\r\\n</sp', 'null', 1, '\r\n### Error updating database.  Cause: java.sql.SQLIntegrityConstraintViolationException: Cannot add or update a child row: a foreign key constraint fails (`ry`.`text_table`, CONSTRAINT `userid` FOREIGN KEY (`userid`) REFERENCES `user_table` (`userid`))\r\n### The error may involve com.ruoyi.system.mapper.TextTableMapper.insertTextTable-Inline\r\n### The error occurred while setting parameters\r\n### SQL: insert into text_table          ( textname,             textcontent,             picture,             csid,             uptime,             favor,             userid )           values ( ?,             ?,             ?,             ?,             ?,             ?,             ? )\r\n### Cause: java.sql.SQLIntegrityConstraintViolationException: Cannot add or update a child row: a foreign key constraint fails (`ry`.`text_table`, CONSTRAINT `userid` FOREIGN KEY (`userid`) REFERENCES `user_table` (`userid`))\n; Cannot add or update a child row: a foreign key constraint fails (`ry`.`text_table`, CONSTRAINT `userid` FOREIGN KEY (`userid`) REFERENCES `user_table` (`userid`)); nested exception is java.sql.SQLIntegrityConstraintViolationException: Cannot add or update a child row: a foreign key constraint fails (`ry`.`text_table`, CONSTRAINT `userid` FOREIGN KEY (`userid`) REFERENCES `user_table` (`userid`))', '2020-10-22 19:56:50');
